          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-05-08T16:54:42Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Aerotropolis Act of 2015</b></p> <p> Amends the Safe, Accountable, Flexible, Efficient Transportation Equity Act: A Legacy for Users (SAFETEA-LU) to extend the eligibility for projects of national and regional significance under the surface transportation grant program to certain aerotropolis transportation system projects.</p> <p>Defines &quot;aerotropolis transportation system&quot; as a planned and coordinated multimodal freight and passenger transportation network that provides efficient, sustainable, and intermodal connectivity to a defined region of economic significance centered around a major airport.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-04-23T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
